# GameSpeed — environment variable contract
#
# This project is a fully client-side React game deployed to GitHub Pages.
# It requires NO server-side env vars at runtime.
#
# The only Vite-time variable that controls deployment behaviour is:
#   VITE_BASE_URL (read via import.meta.env.BASE_URL, set by `base` in vite.config.ts)
#
# If you add backend services in the future, document them here, e.g.:
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key
# VITE_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_live_...
# VITE_POSTHOG_KEY=phc_...
